  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "This package captures the V&V 40 credibility evidence for a CFD model predicting hemolysis in the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. The model has been applied in clinical research contexts to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II cardiopulmonary bypass device at Model Risk Level 2. A full 13-factor assessment was conducted: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). Package conforms to the Minimal profile; structured context-of-use fields are not required under this profile.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-worst-case-hemolysis",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-generic-centrifugal-blood-pump-cfd",
