    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out under MRL 2 requirements. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility to identify worst-case operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in CPB applications. The assessment team accepts this model for the stated decision question.",
